GNU Guix
********

This document describes GNU Guix version 1.5.0, a functional package
management tool written for the GNU system.

   This manual is also available in Simplified Chinese (*note
(guix.zh_CN)Top::), French (*note (guix.fr)Top::), German (*note
(guix.de)Top::), Spanish (*note (guix.es)Top::), Italian (*note
(guix.it)Top::), Brazilian Portuguese (*note (guix.pt_BR)Top::), and
Russian (*note (guix.ru)Top::).  If you would like to translate it in
your native language, consider joining Weblate
(https://translate.codeberg.org/projects/guix/documentation-manual)
(*note Translating Guix::).

* Menu:

* Introduction::                What is Guix about?
* Installation::                Installing Guix.
* System Installation::         Installing the whole operating system.
* Getting Started::             Your first steps.
* Package Management::          Package installation, upgrade, etc.
* Channels::                    Customizing the package collection.
* Development::                 Guix-aided software development.
